03:11.233 --> 03:13.277
It was very clever
to write it in Latin.

03:13.361 --> 03:16.030
<i>With the repeated use
of the passive periphrastic?</i>

03:16.113 --> 03:17.948
That's quite profligate.

03:18.032 --> 03:20.993
And how I was
sending Cicero
with alliterative adjectives

03:21.077 --> 03:22.995
thrusting themselves
into the verbs?

03:23.079 --> 03:24.413
