Lingua sed torpet,
tenuis sub artis.

03:55.069 --> 03:58.948
Flama deanat sonitu suopte.

03:59.031 --> 04:01.450
Catullus 51,
the Lesbia cycle, yes.

04:01.534 --> 04:04.870
