<i>(male)
Let's get some vitals.</i>

01:34:40.217 --> 01:34:41.677
<i>378. Give me
a line there.</i>

01:34:41.760 --> 01:34:43.136
<i>Here you go.</i>

01:34:48.183 --> 01:34:50.853
<i>(female)
Open it up.</i>

01:34:54.147 --> 01:34:56.650
<i>(Doctor)
You folks wanna
come with me?</i>

01:35:03.949 --> 01:35:07.160
Now the arrow missed
his heart by an inch

01:35:07.244 --> 01:35:10.038
and his spine
by centimeters.

01:35:10.122 --> 01:35:13.083
So, what does this
mean for him?

01:35:13.166 --> 01:35:15.627
Well, it'll be
a long recovery.

01:35:17.212 --> 01:35:19.631
I guess I don't need
to tell you this.

01:35:19.715 --> 01:35:22.134
<i>But you saved his life.</i>

01:35:28.348 --> 01:35:30.309
<i>[thunder]</i>

01:35:37.566 --> 01:35:39.234
[baby cries]

01:35:39.318 --> 01:35:41.069
<i>(female)
Yes, yes, yeah.</i>

01:35:42.571 --> 01:35:44.948
Billy, it's fixin' to rain.

01:35:47.951 --> 01:35:49.244
Thanks, Mom.

01:36:02.674 --> 01:36:04.676
You know,

01:36:04.760 --> 01:36:07.638
I think
I'm just gonna sit
here for awhile.

01:36:07.721 --> 01:36:09.348
In the rain?

01:36:12.643 --> 01:36:17.022
I used to be so scared
of these summer storms.

01:36:17.105 --> 01:36:20.817
And then when I went
east, I missed them.

01:36:20.943 --> 01:36:24.404
<i>I was so frightened that
I used to hide in the closet
and cover my ears.</i>

01:36:24.488 --> 01:36:26.615
And I hated that.

01:36:27.741 --> 01:36:30.535
So I went to the library

01:36:30.619 --> 01:36:32.704
and I studied them.

01:36:32.788 --> 01:36:35.874
I learned everything
I could about them ,

01:36:35.958 --> 01:36:38.377
how they happened ,
what made them happen ,

01:36:38.460 --> 01:36:40.671
<i>the name of every cloud.</i>

01:36:40.754 --> 01:36:41.797
And?

01:36:44.466 --> 01:36:46.468
They still happened.

01:36:47.886 --> 01:36:50.973
You mind if I stay
out here with you?

01:36:52.057 --> 01:36:54.059
I wish you would.

01:36:54.142 --> 01:36:56.770
<i>[soft guitar music]</i>
